SELECT projection_status.projection_name, projection_status.last_rebuild_started_at, projection_status.last_rebuild_finished_at, projection_status.last_rebuild_duration_seconds, projection_status.last_rebuild_success, projection_status.last_rebuild_error, projection_status.updated_at 
FROM projection_status 
WHERE projection_status.projection_name = %(projection_name_1)s::VARCHAR

SELECT search_outbox_events.id, search_outbox_events.entity_type, search_outbox_events.entity_id, search_outbox_events.op, search_outbox_events.event_version, search_outbox_events.created_at, search_outbox_events.status, search_outbox_events.owner, search_outbox_events.lease_until, search_outbox_events.attempts, search_outbox_events.next_retry_at, search_outbox_events.updated_at, search_outbox_events.processed_at, search_outbox_events.processing_started_at, search_outbox_events.error_reason, search_outbox_events.error, search_outbox_events.traceparent, search_outbox_events.tracestate, search_outbox_events.replay_count, search_outbox_events.last_replayed_at, search_outbox_events.last_replayed_by, search_outbox_events.last_replayed_reason 
FROM search_outbox_events 
WHERE search_outbox_events.processed_at IS NULL AND search_outbox_events.status = %(status_1)s::VARCHAR AND (search_outbox_events.next_retry_at IS NULL OR search_outbox_events.next_retry_at <= %(next_retry_at_1)s::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE) ORDER BY search_outbox_events.event_version ASC 
 LIMIT %(param_1)s::INTEGER FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED

SELECT count(*) AS count_1 
FROM search_outbox_events 
WHERE search_outbox_events.processed_at IS NULL AND search_outbox_events.status IN (%(status_1_1)s::VARCHAR, %(status_1_2)s::VARCHAR, %(status_1_3)s::VARCHAR)

SELECT count(*) AS count_1 
FROM search_outbox_events 
WHERE search_outbox_events.processed_at IS NULL AND search_outbox_events.status = %(status_1)s::VARCHAR

SELECT count(*) AS count_1 
FROM search_outbox_events 
WHERE search_outbox_events.processed_at IS NULL AND search_outbox_events.status = %(status_1)s::VARCHAR AND (search_outbox_events.lease_until IS NOT NULL AND search_outbox_events.lease_until < %(lease_until_1)s::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE OR search_outbox_events.processing_started_at IS NOT NULL AND search_outbox_events.processing_started_at < %(processing_started_at_1)s::TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE)

SELECT min(search_outbox_events.created_at) AS min_1 
FROM search_outbox_events 
WHERE search_outbox_events.processed_at IS NULL AND search_outbox_events.status IN (%(status_1_1)s::VARCHAR, %(status_1_2)s::VARCHAR, %(status_1_3)s::VARCHAR)
